name: Winter park landscape II
description: Winter park landscape II is a painting of a winter landscape with snow. You can see a park with a snow-covered meadow in the foreground. A path cuts through the snow, which is flanked by a tree. The silhouette of a town is visible on the horizon. Which directs the view to the sky. On the horizon behind the clouds, the yellow light of the sun can be seen. The sky is dominated by clouds.
